New 
@CDCMMWR
 finds most of the nearly 13 million Americans vaccinated in the first month of the #COVID19 vaccination program were women, 50 or older, & non-Hispanic White. Public health officials should ensure that vaccine is administered equitably. More: http://bit.ly/MMWR2121.

New in 
@CDCMMWR
: The percentage of skilled nursing staff vaccinated against #COVID19 was about half of residents vaccinated. Determining reasons for lower vaccination rates and developing communication resources can help increase vaccination of staff. http://bit.ly/MMWR2121b

